Description:
A veteran warrior is tending his wounds on what looks like a battlefield between the navy and the pirates. He tells you that you are late, as the pirates have already been defeated.

When you inform him that you are adventurers on your way to a mission, he laughs and tells you that he used to be an adventurer too, until he found Velkarath Colosseum and became the most famous secutor the arena ever knew.

He is retired now but misses the heat of battle, though he knows that someday his lust for battle will be greater than his strength. However, if you prove yourselves good attackers, he may give you a special arena badge to challenge Velkarath coliseum’s special trial.
DescriptionAction: Do you want the arena badge that he is offering?
